*ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r1 (7 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r1 ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r1.ebuild :
  IBM JDK now tells Portage that it provides a virtual/jdk-1.3 and 
  virtual/jre-1.3. This means that is a proper Blackdown/Sun replacement for
  those who prefer the IBM JDK.

